OL,3,CCould Jersey and Guernsey become
OL,4,C'Crown Territories'?
OL,6,FA senior politician in says the island
OL,7,Fneeds to "be prepared" for a move away
OL,8,Ffrom the UK in the future, amid calls
OL,9,Fto change the term 'Crown
OL,10,FDependencies'.
OL,12,FThe former Bailiff of Jersey and the
OL,13,Fcivil head of the island, Sir Philip
OL,14,FBailhache, told ITV News: "We have to
OL,15,Falways look at what is in the interest
OL,16,Fof Jersey.
OL,18,F"At the moment I think the interests
OL,19,Fof Jersey are served by being in a
OL,20,Frelationship with the United Kingdom
OL,21,Fbut that may not always be the case."
