OL,3,CCould Jersey and Guernsey become
OL,4,C'Crown Territories'?
OL,6,FFor centuries, the island has been
OL,7,Flinked to the UK via the Monarch.
OL,9,FLike the other Crown Dependencies of
OL,10,Fthe Isle of Man and Guernsey, Jersey
OL,11,Fhas its own government, parliament and
OL,12,Flegal systems.
OL,14,FSir Philip also said the term 'Crown
OL,15,FDependencies' should be retired,
OL,16,Fdescribing it as "imperialistic" and
OL,17,Finstead suggesting 'Crown Territories'.
OL,19,FHe added: "Our autonomy really ought
OL,20,Fto be reflected in the word that is
OL,21,Fused to describe the relationship."
