OL,3,CCould Jersey and Guernsey become
OL,4,C'Crown Territories'?
OL,6,FGuernsey's former Chief Minister
OL,7,Fechoed the calls for a name change,
OL,8,Fbut suggested 'Crown Dominions' to
OL,9,Fkeep the collective acronym of 'CDs'.
OL,11,FHe explained: "I struggle to find
OL,12,Fanyone who is really content with the
OL,13,Fterm Crown Dependency, it's a fiction
OL,14,Fwhich has arisen .. .and nobody really
OL,15,Fquite knows the origin.
OL,17,F"In reality, we are not really
OL,18,Fdependent on anyone."
