OL,3,CCould Jersey and Guernsey become
OL,4,C'Crown Territories'?
OL,6,FJersey's External Relations Minister
OL,7,FDeputy Ian Gorst said the island is
OL,8,F"open to discussions on a potential
OL,9,Fchange to the name".
OL,11,FHe added the government would "need to
OL,12,Fdiscuss this with our colleagues in
OL,13,FGuernsey and the Isle of Man" and
OL,14,Fwould only move forward if there was
OL,15,F"unanimity" on the subject.
OL,17,FThe Crown Dependencies are distinct
OL,18,Ffrom the 14 British Overseas
OL,19,FTerritories, which include Bermuda,
OL,20,Fthe Falkland Islands and Gibraltar.
